<BaseLayout title="About Us" lang="en" path="about/" active="about">
  <div class="container section prose">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p><em>Placeholder copy — replace with the press's real introduction.</em></p>
    <p>
      East-West Press (EWP) is an independent academic publisher based in the United
      States. Our mission is to promote dialogues and exchanges between East and West by
      publishing rigorous, accessible scholarship that crosses linguistic and cultural
      boundaries.
    </p>
    <h2>What We Publish</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Humanities — philosophy, history, literature, and religious studies</li>
      <li>Social sciences — politics, economics, and society</li>
      <li>Asian studies — China, East Asia, and the Asian diaspora</li>
      <li>Global studies — cross-cultural and comparative research</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>For Authors</h2>
    <p>
      We welcome proposals for monographs, edited volumes, and translations. Please send
      a brief prospectus and CV to
      <a href="mailto:info@kfbook.org">info@kfbook.org</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
